  "texts": [
    "Table 3 gives an overview of the 40 tabular data sets we use for our study.",
    "Note that this number is significantly higher compared to the 4 to 5 data sets that are used in previous studies of the disagreement problem (see Table 1).",
    "This allows us to confidently make more general conclusions.",
    "A test set is created for each data set by comprising 20% of the data with a minimum of 200 instances.",
    "This means that e.g., for the threeOf9 data set, we do not use 102 instances in the test set, but we use 200."
  ],
